    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system that has been meticulously serviced. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative upgrade\u2014and a factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications, delivering the precise turn-in and mechanical grip these M-chassis are renowned for. With a limited-slip differential providing optimal torque distribution and a pristine interior free of bolster wear, this is a turn-key example for the purist seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
